# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../preferences.rst:268
msgid ""
"To reset **all** preferences to their default values, please delete the "
"``openshot.settings`` file and re-launch OpenShot. The settings file can be "
"located at this path: ``~/.openshot_qt/openshot.settings`` or ``C:"
